name: TRASH PAINT GOES DIGITAL on FOUNDATION

metadata.name: BREAK THE INTERNET KIM KarTRASHian
metadata.description:
The Queen of Trash TV is now gracing the cover of the Summer 2022 edition of TRASH!


Life has been the dumps for KIM KarTRASHian ever since Trash Kan-Ye and her split up. They were perfect together. So sad.

Butt look at her now!

KIM KarTRASHian is ready to BREAK THE INTERNET!

ONLY 1 EDITION!
